                4. **TransparentPanel** — the NSPanel subclass for the floating window. File: apps/swift/Shared/Sources/Shared/Components/TransparentPanel.swift

                5. **ChatPlugin** — how messages are sent, how responses come back, the sendMessage flow, isSending state. File: apps/swift/Shared/Sources/Shared/Plugins/ChatPlugin/ChatPlugin.swift

                6. Find any existing streaming/typing animation code, loading indicators, or status bar components.

                Search thoroughly in apps/swift/Shared/Sources/Shared/ for all related components.
